sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Script as init-letsencrypt.sh
    participant Compose as Docker Compose
    participant Nginx
    participant Stack as api / worker / frontend / redis
    participant Certbot
    participant LE as Let's Encrypt

    Admin->>Script: ./init-letsencrypt.sh
    Script->>Nginx: Render HTTP-only config
    Script->>Compose: up -d redis api worker frontend nginx
    Compose->>Stack: Start containers

    Script->>Certbot: certonly --webroot -d DOMAIN
    Certbot->>Nginx: Serve /.well-known/acme-challenge/
    Nginx->>LE: HTTP-01 challenge
    LE-->>Certbot: Issue certificate

    Script->>Nginx: Render HTTPS config
    Script->>Nginx: nginx -s reload
    Script->>Compose: up -d certbot
    Note over Certbot: Renews every 12h

    Admin->>Nginx: https://elgenius.duckdns.org/
